title: Taxis and Public Transportation
description:
Taxi Service

Taxis are available at the Taxi stand outside the terminal.
Rates:
$2.85 - Initial flag drop, including first 1/9th mile or 30 seconds or fraction thereof
$0.30 - Each additional 1/9th mile or part
$0.30 - Each 37 seconds waiting time and/or traffic delay ($29.19/hour wait)

Please visit Long Beach Yellow Cab's website at www.longbeachyellowcab.com.
